description:
Bytescout BarCode Reader SDK for .NET, ASP.NET and ActiveX 

(c) ByteScout, 2008-2012

Bytescout BarCode Reader SDK provides functionality for reading barcodes from images (BMP, JPG, PNG, TIF, GIF)

Works in .NET, ASP.NET, Compact Framework 2.00 (Pocket PC and Window CE), ActiveX, x64, Command Line 

Benefits: 

- Supports 1D barcode types to read from images and photo files: Code128, Code39 (including extended and TriOptic), EAN13, EAN8, I2of5, UPCA, UPCE, GS1, Codabar;
- Supports 2D barcode types to read from images and photo files: PDF417, Datamatrix, QR Code, Aztec;
- Barcode reader returns: barcode symbology type, recognized string and barcode location points;
- Supports reading of multiple barcodes from one image; 
- reads PDF files (without any other tools!);
- Supports multipaged TIFF images as input to read barcodes from; 
- Supports: .NET 2.00, CF.NET 2.00 (Windows CE and Pocket PC), ActiveX, ASP.NET (including Medium Trust mode);

TRAIL VERSION LIMITATIONS:
 - adds reminder text message into output barcode value

